OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome hazy evening sunshine to end the
OL,7,Fday, Some clear spells overnight with
OL,8,Fvariable cloud around to the north.
OL,9,FSome isolated mist or fog patches
OL,10,Flikely to form in prone spots. Light
OL,11,Fto moderate northwesterly winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FA day of variable cloud and
OL,14,Fsome bright or sunny spells once any
OL,15,Fearly morning mist or fog clears.
OL,16,FFeeling warm in the light to moderate
OL,17,Fwinds.
