OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FFurther
OL,6,Fvery warm sunshine on Saturday.
OL,7,FConditions turning more changeable
OL,8,Finto Sunday, with some showery and
OL,9,Fbreezy weather moving through from the
OL,10,Fnorthwest. Mostly dry but quite cloudy
OL,11,Fon Monday.
